title: Code Monkey Save World 02 (of 04) (2013) (digital) (Son of Ultro
description: When Code Monkey's office crush was kidnapped by Laura the Robo Queen, it seemed like a smart move to team up with the world's most ruthless supervillain in order to rescue her. But Code Monkey's supervillain partner has some shocking secrets of his own that throw the whole plan in peril! Featuring the origin of Skullcrusher! And the secret history of Code Monkey!
